survey_response.review_text: I had gone to Dr Priyanka Kalra for RCT treatment for my left tooth which was badly infected along with some mild pain for 7-10 days. The doctor explained to me the complete treatment protocol in detail and finalized a convenient date for RCT procedure once my infection had subsided. The entire procedure was conducted with utmost care and precaution to ensure that I did not face any discomfort, whatsoever. Further, the doctor was also explaining to me at each stage, the various steps of how procedure was being conducted, which put me at ease. I was also impressed by the hygiene of this clinic and the friendliness of the support staff. I shall highly recommend Simplismile clinic for all Dental procedures. Post this RCT, I am planning a tooth implantation procedure here.
